description: Medicare fee-for-service data for each county broken out by aged, disabled, and ESRD beneficiaries including data on total Medicare fee-for-service reimbursement and enrollment for Parts A and B, the corresponding per capita reimbursement, for Part A, reimbursement for direct (DME) and indirect medical education (IME) expenditures and disproportionate share expenditures (DSH), and the per capita expenditures with the medical education and disproportionate share expenditures removed.
